In a central London pub, Guy

00:00:57.660 --> 00:01:00.000
Burgess finished off his drink.

00:01:00.620 --> 00:01:03.270
The air was thick with the smell of

00:01:03.270 --> 00:01:06.330
cigarette smoke, sweat and frothy beer.

00:01:07.520 --> 00:01:09.920
Conversation rumbled on in the background,

00:01:10.260 --> 00:01:12.870
chair legs screeched on the wooden floor.

00:01:14.017 --> 00:01:17.137
